			<p>The films <extref href="https://media.library.cornell.edu/media/Whatcha+Doin%27+MamaA+Part+1/1_ttnawqj0/7781881"> <title>Whatcha Doin' Mama Part 1 </title> </extref> and <extref href="https://media.library.cornell.edu/media/Whatcha+Doin%27+MamaA+Part+2/1_yhwd3wy8/7781881"> <title>Whatcha Doin' Mama Part 2 </title> </extref>from this collection have been digitized and can be found on Cornell's Library Media Space website along with other Home Economics and related films.</p>
